Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.70,0:00:03.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳跟阿衛進展得如何了？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.40,0:00:06.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年夏天一點進展也沒有啊\N拜託，報告都還沒寫完耶
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.34,0:00:09.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼沒有找我啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.21,0:00:12.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找了啊!找了好多次耶!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.31,0:00:15.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打妳手機妳也不接
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.28,0:00:17.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是很傷腦筋耶
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.52,0:00:20.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過，深優同學她啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.89,0:00:22.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很強喔，那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.65,0:00:23.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.82,0:00:25.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人造人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.22,0:00:26.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機器人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.39,0:00:27.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,改造人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.03,0:00:28.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.03,0:00:31.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以確定她不是人類
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.46,0:00:33.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"蕃薯煮…芋頭？"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.53,0:00:36.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得好像惡劣的笑話一樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.80,0:00:40.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,操縱無依者的少女…人造人…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.07,0:00:42.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鎖定HiME的神秘黑暗組織
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.17,0:00:44.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,氣氛炒熱起來了啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.91,0:00:47.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有種陰謀終於現形了的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.78,0:00:50.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過深優同學跟艾莉莎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.55,0:00:51.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.72,0:00:54.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西爾斯財團那群人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.29,0:00:58.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎從很久以前就開始調查\NHiME能力相關情報
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.06,0:01:02.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不認為他們會這麼輕易罷手
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.29,0:01:03.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要多加留心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.90,0:01:10.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,班會已經要開始了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.34,0:01:13.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別在第二學期第一天就蹺課啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.37,0:01:14.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.87,0:01:17.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岩境製藥嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.74,0:01:20.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.29,0:01:39.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這片朗朗晴空裡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.53,0:01:46.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將我們的心情 飛散灑滿其中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.01,0:01:51.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果命中註定的那個人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.14,0:01:54.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能夠是你那該有多好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.55,0:02:00.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是現實卻無法如願以償
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.12,0:02:06.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在閃耀光芒的風裡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.32,0:02:12.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夢想的羽毛 飄然落下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.73,0:02:17.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鼓起勇氣邁向未來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.44,0:02:21.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 就這麼美麗地前進
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.94,0:02:29.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始奔騰的熱烈心跳
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.51,0:02:36.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,躍動出跟那一天同樣的速度
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.89,0:02:42.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡你率直的眼神
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.86,0:02:48.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望能永遠看著你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.37,0:02:56.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我，舞衣，命仔，玖我同學
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.44,0:02:58.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第13話 ～玉響之夜～\N奈緒，修女…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.81,0:03:02.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第13話 ～玉響之夜～\N還有告知了玖我同學狀況的\N神秘人士 「黛安娜」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.38,0:03:04.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第13話 ～玉響之夜～\N救了楯一命\N那個操縱青蛙怪的人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.48,0:03:07.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,8個人了啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.29,0:03:08.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那應該還剩下4人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.95,0:03:09.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,4人？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.66,0:03:13.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我猜想HiME總共有12個人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.83,0:03:14.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果艾莉莎…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.99,0:03:17.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說也有點怪怪的了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.50,0:03:20.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她也是HiME的話，那就還有3人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.17,0:03:26.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,HiME究竟是什麼啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.40,0:03:29.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是在調查這個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.14,0:03:30.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於HiME的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.94,0:03:35.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及在這塊封架之地上\N不斷反覆上演的戰姬神事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.55,0:03:37.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不斷反覆上演？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.48,0:03:40.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞衣妳也看過\N神社裡面的壁畫對吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.02,0:03:45.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每數百年\N就會舉行一次HiME的神事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.46,0:03:46.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這點是肯定的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.36,0:03:50.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.76,0:03:52.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的不可以\N把那件事情說出去嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.50,0:03:53.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.77,0:03:54.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該說
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.07,0:03:57.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是妳看到的幻影吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.20,0:03:58.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我根本沒看見啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.60,0:03:59.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是看見了啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.64,0:04:00.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅紅的眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.94,0:04:02.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這～麼尖的牙齒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.77,0:04:04.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳睡昏了吧妳
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.51,0:04:09.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我不說，相對的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.98,0:04:14.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞衣學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.76,0:04:23.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞衣學姐她怎麼了啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.63,0:04:25.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.57,0:04:29.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳跟楯阿一怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.20,0:04:31.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.90,0:04:36.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之\N跟HiME有關的事情就交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.84,0:04:40.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我打算在魂響祭典的時候\N去採訪封架神社
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.65,0:04:42.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魂…什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.15,0:04:43.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳不知道啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.72,0:04:45.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魂？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.42,0:04:49.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳這樣也算是個16歲的少女嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.49,0:04:51.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是知道妳很多事情要忙啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.06,0:04:53.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我覺得稍微犯點桃花
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.86,0:04:55.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不會遭受報應吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.49,0:05:00.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,16歲的戀愛\N只有在16歲才能談啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.60,0:05:06.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.87,0:05:08.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好，好的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.31,0:05:11.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好積極，好積極
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.11,0:05:12.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魂響祭典這東西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.94,0:05:15.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這附近算是相當有名的祭典
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.38,0:05:17.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然重心是落在封架神社上…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.88,0:05:20.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過這裡也是很受歡迎的景點
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.32,0:05:22.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.12,0:05:24.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祭典明明就是明天才開始
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.46,0:05:27.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不守規矩的人\N還真是抓也抓不完
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.39,0:05:31.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平常若像這樣\N可是會被執行部給拆除掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.20,0:05:34.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實，這間水晶宮\N可是有傳說的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.03,0:05:38.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在緞帶上寫著對方的名字\N然後把它繫到欄杆上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.47,0:05:39.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二個人就可以在一起了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.47,0:05:43.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞衣同學，妳好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.21,0:05:44.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黎人學長…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.14,0:05:48.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祭典那天，已經有什麼安排嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.21,0:05:50.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目…目前還沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.05,0:05:52.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼，鴇羽舞衣同學
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.05,0:05:56.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一天可不可以跟我約會呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.65,0:05:57.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約會？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.16,0:06:06.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後呢？妳打算怎麼回應？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.50,0:06:07.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然要拒絕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.07,0:06:09.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理由為何？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.80,0:06:11.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.24,0:06:14.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還要打工…\N妳剛才不是說沒事做嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.31,0:06:17.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊，該怎麼辦呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.68,0:06:19.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞衣!妳聽說了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.38,0:06:20.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.18,0:06:21.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.75,0:06:25.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼，妳也有打算要綁啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.52,0:06:27.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說，妳要寫誰的名字啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.95,0:06:29.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞衣啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.19,0:06:31.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝，我高興得要哭出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.96,0:06:33.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不只是妳喔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.52,0:06:34.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有雪之啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.59,0:06:35.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千繪啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.53,0:06:36.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葵呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.46,0:06:38.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外還有詩帆跟奈緒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.40,0:06:39.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及黎人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.83,0:06:43.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡這種感情很棒!對吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.40,0:06:45.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.71,0:06:50.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正你什麼忙也幫不上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.91,0:06:51.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就別管我了!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.64,0:07:21.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎樣都跟你無關吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.24,0:07:25.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊，跟我無關
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.96,0:07:44.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為舞衣學姐說過\N要支持我和哥哥的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.47,0:07:48.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情況如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.47,0:07:51.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我很怕\N不過他真的很溫柔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.27,0:07:53.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有種真的被愛的感覺唷
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.48,0:08:00.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,詩帆我…沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.35,0:08:04.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果哥哥想那麼做的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.05,0:08:09.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.49,0:08:12.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭啦，好丟臉，色鬼～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.06,0:08:17.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有看到檔案的內容嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.93,0:08:20.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能夠駭出來的只有目錄而已
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.50,0:08:25.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是在 「風華學園」 目錄底下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.44,0:08:27.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實有看到 「日暮茜」 的檔案
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.44,0:08:32.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為何會有她…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.16,0:08:49.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.29,0:08:54.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對我來說\N現在最重要的就是巧海嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.20,0:08:58.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光因為自己是HiME什麼的\N就夠容易碰到麻煩事情了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.77,0:09:02.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪有閒工夫去管\N其他有的沒的雜事啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.41,0:09:07.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟一直都很麻煩妳
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.38,0:09:10.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我答應要幫晶做…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.45,0:09:13.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以，明天開始就…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.92,0:09:17.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我有跟他說\N不用麻煩了啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.32,0:09:19.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那，晶的份也讓我來…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.82,0:09:20.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.69,0:09:23.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可也不能
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.19,0:09:26.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老是給姊姊添麻煩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.93,0:09:29.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.43,0:09:31.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.20,0:09:34.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實在吸血鬼事件的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.67,0:09:37.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要我去巡邏\N相對的你會幫我做便當
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.91,0:09:41.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過這樣真的好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.58,0:09:44.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你姊姊，打擊很大喔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.35,0:09:46.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.25,0:09:47.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的還是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.09,0:09:50.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太依賴姊姊了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.09,0:09:54.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得漸漸地試著去完成\N自己可以做到的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.86,0:09:59.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好，說得好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.10,0:10:02.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣才像個男子漢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.37,0:10:05.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能問…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.10,0:10:07.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳的答案嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.97,0:10:11.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼…呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.35,0:10:18.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.49,0:10:24.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿和服比想像中還花時間…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.39,0:10:27.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常適合妳唷
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.60,0:10:32.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小命也是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.80,0:10:36.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然還是帶著拖油瓶啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.63,0:10:38.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真搞不過她喔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.37,0:10:42.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿浴衣的黎人學長好帥～
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.14,0:10:44.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過，那個樣子\N簡直就是爸媽帶小孩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.51,0:10:46.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的也是呢～
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.14,0:10:50.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這樣特地拄著枴杖出來\N就沒什麼意義了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.25,0:10:52.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那，我們就去管點閒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.42,0:10:57.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天爸爸跟媽媽都不在
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.16,0:11:00.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,詩帆加油!妳很可愛喔!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.93,0:11:07.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人家…是認真的喔…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.77,0:11:12.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞衣!那個!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.84,0:11:13.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還～沒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.04,0:11:15.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到學校之前先忍著
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.06,0:11:36.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈囉，小命
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.56,0:11:39.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命～
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.96,0:11:41.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小命～
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.70,0:11:44.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子真是的\N只是一個不注意就…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.24,0:11:50.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（小命在我手上）\N（想要我還給妳）
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.24,0:11:52.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（就給我好好去約會）\N（By 好管閒事之人）
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.72,0:11:59.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.25,0:12:03.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的，哪有人硬是約人出來\N自己還遲到的啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.63,0:12:18.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快…快快…快走啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.40,0:12:19.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要拖拖拉拉的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.61,0:12:27.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在風華學園擔任日本史教師
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.11,0:12:29.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名叫杉浦碧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.25,0:12:30.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.71,0:12:33.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是不是有\N在什麼地方見過妳啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.02,0:12:35.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有…有嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.09,0:12:41.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目標是地下4樓
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.26,0:12:42.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該是那裡沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.41,0:13:02.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了，舞衣同學\N有沒有什麼要求呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.81,0:13:04.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.45,0:13:07.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我約出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.32,0:13:09.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既不是巧海的姊姊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.29,0:13:11.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不是小命的監護人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.89,0:13:14.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是小我兩歲的可愛學妹
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.93,0:13:17.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以不用客氣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.03,0:13:19.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果妳不耍點小任性
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.70,0:13:22.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反而會讓\N硬是約妳出來的我困擾
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.77,0:13:24.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黎人學長…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.97,0:13:32.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遜腳，拿來給我啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.05,0:13:40.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是神秘的忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.78,0:13:42.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙，在取笑我嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.69,0:13:43.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒這回事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.95,0:13:45.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡～
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.72,0:13:49.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也得好好享樂一番\N不能輸給他們喔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.46,0:13:51.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.96,0:13:56.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距離蝕已經剩下不多時間了哪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.70,0:13:58.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快趁現在…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.10,0:14:00.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好享受吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.81,0:14:04.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.81,0:14:05.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稀客，稀客
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.98,0:14:07.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理…理事長？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.75,0:14:10.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杉浦老師，晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.71,0:14:14.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宗像先生，我今年也來參拜了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.02,0:14:16.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請自便
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.46,0:14:22.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她每年都會來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.36,0:14:26.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了，關於祭典的事情啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.87,0:14:29.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個魂響祭典
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.53,0:14:34.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是以本地流傳的\N戰姬傳說為基礎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.24,0:14:38.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了守護所愛之人而戰
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.71,0:14:44.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,度過短暫而空虛的人生\N斷送生命的少女們啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.38,0:14:49.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學校水晶宮的祈願儀式
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.25,0:14:56.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是由來自戰姬們將頭巾\N綁在生長在那兒的樹木上
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.63,0:15:00.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在面臨最終決戰之前
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.30,0:15:05.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祈禱自己能夠\N與所愛的男性再次相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.57,0:15:09.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（一人限一條緞帶）\N（請為負責整理的工作人員著想）
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.54,0:15:10.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（12點以後禁止許願）\N（風華學園 執行部）
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.88,0:15:15.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.58,0:15:17.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我跟哥哥…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.42,0:15:21.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小遙妳不繫嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.02,0:15:24.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己給自己增加工作\N還嫌不夠忙喔？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.26,0:15:27.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說得…也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.80,0:15:33.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全不害臊耶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.83,0:15:35.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對象應該是玖我同學吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.43,0:15:38.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又不是什麼有求必"音"的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.60,0:15:39.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是有求必應
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.07,0:15:42.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會長？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.34,0:15:43.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳說什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.71,0:15:52.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小命妳要繫幾條啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.72,0:15:54.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我喜歡每個人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.72,0:15:56.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有千繪和葵的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.79,0:15:57.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.36,0:16:00.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過這種情況下的喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.06,0:16:03.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一點不一樣吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.23,0:16:05.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡還有分一樣不一樣的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.60,0:16:09.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該…該怎麼解釋呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.43,0:16:10.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.37,0:16:13.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這條叫做金一
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.34,0:16:16.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這條紅的叫凸眼妹
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.98,0:16:19.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣子看起來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.64,0:16:21.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳還是跟幼稚園時一樣沒變呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.35,0:16:25.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳果然還是個孩子哪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.38,0:16:28.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦，事情也辦完了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.35,0:16:29.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回家去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.02,0:16:32.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人家已經不是小孩子了…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.66,0:16:38.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,詩帆已經不是小孩了!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.36,0:16:40.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.96,0:16:41.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,詩帆，別這樣!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.00,0:16:42.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.34,0:16:49.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,詩帆…已經是大人了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.84,0:16:52.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.01,0:16:55.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.35,0:17:02.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.85,0:17:05.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得我好像太任性\N跟你要了不少東西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.82,0:17:06.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這小意思
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.52,0:17:09.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞衣同學能玩得開心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.03,0:17:11.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才是最重要的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.60,0:17:14.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.06,0:17:15.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.87,0:17:16.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.53,0:17:21.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得妳最近\N好像沒什麼精神
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.47,0:17:23.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒這回事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.54,0:17:25.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直都很…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.51,0:17:26.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吸血鬼事件…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.31,0:17:30.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生…什麼事了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.12,0:17:42.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不想說的話可以不用說
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.56,0:17:45.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過，應該結束了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.03,0:17:48.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那件事情已經結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.87,0:17:51.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過，一定會有\N相同的事情再度發生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.84,0:17:54.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.14,0:17:56.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就到此為止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.07,0:17:58.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別再跟我有所牽扯了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.61,0:18:04.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳打算就這樣，跟大家疏遠
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.35,0:18:06.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後一個人活下去嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.85,0:18:10.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳總是把巧海的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.02,0:18:13.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有妳的力量的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.19,0:18:14.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個人默默扛下來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.83,0:18:16.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後還要勉強擠出笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.66,0:18:20.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能說的話，不說無妨
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.20,0:18:23.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，別勉強裝出沒事的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.54,0:18:26.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難過的話，就說難過
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.60,0:18:28.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想哭的話就哭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.88,0:18:35.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.38,0:18:37.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撐得住妳
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.55,0:18:41.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黎人…學長
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.12,0:18:47.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥，會痛耶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.41,0:19:09.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鴇羽!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.70,0:19:33.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很漂亮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.57,0:19:36.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是為了阿和而打扮的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.17,0:19:40.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為，人家對阿和啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.18,0:19:43.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的，不要不講話啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.45,0:19:47.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿和啊，回答我嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.18,0:19:49.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫你回答我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.25,0:19:50.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好嘛，阿和…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.89,0:19:52.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿和？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.29,0:19:54.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿和？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.76,0:20:01.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,楯…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.70,0:20:04.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不，不是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.64,0:20:06.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個，我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.37,0:20:08.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.21,0:20:10.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳要對楯解釋？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.21,0:20:14.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,楯你也是，為什麼妨礙我們？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.45,0:20:19.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們果然…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.32,0:20:28.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪有!我，我是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.76,0:20:30.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.80,0:20:34.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.90,0:20:37.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人的吧…？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.00,0:20:39.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.07,0:20:46.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞衣學姐妳也真過份
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.21,0:20:50.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳不是說過\N會支持我跟哥哥的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.15,0:20:54.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙子!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.32,0:20:56.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大騙子!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.59,0:21:33.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西爾斯的…心之子？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.39,0:21:36.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過就是個仿冒HiME
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.06,0:21:38.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還幹得真漂亮…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.27,0:21:46.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蝕一號 ． 月神的瞄準誤差
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.07,0:21:49.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,往東南東偏離兩公尺
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.21,0:21:51.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在許可範圍之內
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.51,0:21:55.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目標已經完全遭到破壞了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.01,0:21:58.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝妳，深優
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.38,0:22:03.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼通告所有黃金艦隊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.49,0:22:07.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前往開啟英靈殿之門…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.06,0:22:14.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「請別迷惘」 這句話\N我說不出口
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.73,0:22:20.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有無法傳達給你的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.51,0:22:26.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太過寂寞的笑容搖擺不定
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.84,0:22:31.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撫過傷口 Lonely good-bye
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.92,0:22:38.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連熱情都會讓我痛楚
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.42,0:22:43.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追尋著永恆的碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.53,0:22:50.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你曾是我的天空我的夢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.33,0:22:54.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將那段燃燒熔化的日子…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.87,0:23:00.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別忘記 要時時想起
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.88,0:23:07.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算只是收藏在心底
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.28,0:23:09.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Search for my life
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.15,0:23:13.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總有一天還會再相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.42,0:23:20.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是喜歡你那清澈的雙眼 現在
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.36,0:23:23.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走上各自的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.67,0:23:26.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重新開始前進
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.18,0:23:40.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被盯上的學園
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.88,0:23:43.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被盯上的學園\N舞衣同學\N出現意外人士干擾了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.42,0:23:44.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被盯上的學園\N好了，我們繼續吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.19,0:23:45.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被盯上的學園\N現在不是\N做這種事情的時候啦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.92,0:23:49.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀，看來我們應該\N再多等一會兒的樣子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.83,0:23:51.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是啊，深優？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.16,0:23:53.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊，真是可惜了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.40,0:23:54.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.04,0:00:00.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.28,0:23:59.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是從幾時開始的呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.08,0:24:01.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當我發覺的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.48,0:24:03.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我總是用雙眼\N追尋著那傢伙的身影
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.25,0:24:07.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,問我為什麼的話\N其實我也搞不太清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.09,0:24:08.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該說有點在意呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.49,0:24:12.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等，我可不是光看胸部啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.76,0:24:15.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確是會\N不知不覺就往那邊看過去啦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.33,0:24:17.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也是沒辦法的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.33,0:24:19.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.64,0:24:21.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次見面的時候真的很糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.14,0:24:25.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每次碰面\N只會說些讓彼此不高興的話
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.11,0:24:29.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.48,0:24:31.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道她是\N自己一個人承擔著很多責任
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.71,0:24:35.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還總是奮力向前\N拼命活下去的人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.09,0:24:37.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概就是因為這樣吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.72,0:24:41.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總是有一種\N無法放著她不管的感覺…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.13,0:24:43.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.26,0:24:44.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戀愛？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.23,0:24:46.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別…別說笑了啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.23,0:24:49.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種這麼愛生氣的粗魯女生\N我才沒興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.20,0:24:51.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.77,0:24:53.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.14,0:24:54.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然還是搞不懂哪
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.97,0:24:57.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在就先暫時這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.21,0:24:59.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然還沒找到答案
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.21,0:25:00.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不想這麼快就下結論啊


